        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Public Health Funding Prevents Pandemics Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases annual funding for the Prevention and Public Health Fund for FY2022-FY2027. This fund supports prevention, wellness, and public health activities carried out by the Department of Health and Human Services, including researching and tracking public health threats. </p>]]>
        </text>
